<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Peter N., Provinzial des Augustinerordens in Alemannien</head><p>Der Rat bittet im Namen des Priors und der Brüder des Augustinerklosters zu Nürnberg um Niederlassung des gebürtigen Nürnbergers Hans Renner zur Predigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_522" id="260v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l17"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> petern
                                <expan>p<ex>ro</ex>uincial</expan> Auguſtiner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l18">ordens in <del rend="strikethrough">Teutſchen landen </del>
<expan>Al<ex>e</ex>ma<ex>n</ex>nia</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_522_r1l19">Erſamer vnd lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Eʒ ſind für vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ der Prior vnd etlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l20">ſein prüder Auguſtiner ordens hie bey vns / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns fürgelegt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l22">vnd gebeten / daʒ vvir ew von pruder Hanſen Renners der auch 
<del rend="strikethrough">ewrs </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_522_r1l21">irs </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l23">ordens vnd der Stat kind hıe iſt / <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllen / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l24">vnd <expan>erlaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / daʒ Er cʒu Jn <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd bey Jn <expan>vvone<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_line_1576348365260_3562">dem volk das 
<del rend="strikethrough">goſw </del> gotſwort ſagen vnd predigen müge / Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l27">daʒ Jr das alſo durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> tun vvöllet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_522_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ man den mıt <expan>ſeın<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">predıg gern höre / das wöllen etc </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_522_line_1576348395719_3577">das wollen etc </ab></add> <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir mainen daʒ Er <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>Cloſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_522_r1l30">hie nücʒer ſeẏ <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein <expan>fremd<ex>er</ex></expan> der niht der Stat kind hie iſt / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_522" id="260v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Petern, <expan>p<ex>ro</ex>vincial</expan>
                        augustiner ordens in <expan>Al<ex>e</ex>ma<ex>n</ex>nia</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> ez sind für uns
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> der prior und etlich sein prüder
                        augustiner ordens hie bey uns und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                        fürgelegt und gebeten, daz wir ew von pruder Hansen Renners, der auch
                            <add>irs</add> ordens und der stat kind hie ist,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen, daz ir im
                                <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>erlaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wöllet, daz er czu in <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> und bey in
                                <expan>wone<ex>n</ex></expan> und dem volk das gotswort sagen und
                        predigen müge. Also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das also durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun wöllet. <add>Das wollen etc</add>.
                                <expan>Wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir mainen, daz er
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>clost<ex>er</ex></expan> hie nüczer sey, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ein <expan>fremd<ex>er</ex></expan> der niht der stat kind hie ist.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
